    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project or a donor for parts. The engine has developed a heavy knock and suffers from chronic overheating and persistent oil leaks. Additionally, the transmission slips significantly under load, and the suspension requires a complete overhaul. The exterior shows its age with noticeable rust, fading paint, and several dents, while the interior has significant wear and tear, including cracked upholstery. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
