      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry, offering exceptional turn-in response and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. This example represents a balanced driver\u2019s car with sorted mechanicals and a clean title.",
      "price": 34500.0,
